data.description: Buyers had a change of heart, so this gorgeous home is back on the market! Welcome home! This 3-bed, 2-full bath gem features open-concept living, stainless steel appliances, a farm-style sink, and granite countertops. Vaulted ceilings enhance the living space, and each bedroom includes a spacious walk-in closet. Step outside to a large backyard surrounded by a cedar privacy fence, complemented by an uncovered patio and a 20x30 cedar gazebo with electricity and a ceiling fan—stamped concrete ties the front driveway to the backyard patio, creating a cohesive design. Conveniently located with easy access to I-35W and US-67, this home offers both tranquility and accessibility. Whether you're relaxing on the patio or entertaining in the gazebo, this property is an oasis of comfort and style. Schedule a viewing now and make this your perfect home! **UP TO 10K IN SELLER CONCESSIONS WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER.**
